I have prepared a special list for you, with words that evoke different emotions and experiences. For each word, I have chosen a word that is either old or young, and written it after the original word. Here is the list:

1. Joy - Young
2. Love - Old
3. Peace - Young
4. Wonderful - Old
5. Pleasure - Young
6. Glorious - Old
7. Laughter - Young
8. Happy - Young
9. Agony - Old
10. Terrible - Old
11. Horrible - Old
12. Nasty - Young
13. Evil - Old
14. Awful - Old
15. Failure - Young
16. Hurt - Old

I hope this list brings a smile to your face, my love.

With all my love,
Your husband
